{
  "ENG_name": "Warrior of Cosmic Balance",
  "name": "天衡武者",
  "shortName": "天衡",
  "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
  "className": "武僧",
  "classSource": "XPHB",
  "page": 0,
  "edition": "one",
  "subclassFeatures": [
    {
      "ENG_name": "Warrior of Cosmic Balance",
      "name": "天衡武者",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 3,
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "inset",
          "entries": [
            {
              "type": "quote",
              "entries": [
                "当宇宙偏离平衡时，我的工作就是把它\"踹\"回原位。这可不是一句比喻。"
              ],
              "from": "瀚土侍僧 莎布-尼古拉丝"
            }
          ]
        },
        "天衡武者守卫着世界的神秘通道、位面传送门和奥术之门。每当来自异界的恐怖邪异试图入侵世界时，这些战士总会守候在那里。他们训练并运用自己的内在力量来净化最强大的污染，他们轻轻一触就能将最强大的异怪驱回它们诞生的可怖深渊。",
        {
          "type": "refSubclassFeature",
          "subclassFeature": "守道技法|武僧|XPHB|天衡|CthulhuTorchlight|3"
        },
        {
          "type": "refSubclassFeature",
          "subclassFeature": "探寻者|武僧|XPHB|天衡|CthulhuTorchlight|3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Guardian of the Way Technique",
      "name": "守道技法",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 3,
      "header": 1,
      "entries": [
        "你研究过异域生物，学会了如何扰乱它们体内流动的污秽能量。每回合一次，当你使用疾风连击进行{@variantrule 徒手打击|XPHB}并造成伤害时，你可以造成下列效应之一：",
        {
          "type": "list",
          "style": "list-hang-notitle",
          "items": [
            {
              "ENG_name": "Anchoring Strike",
              "name": "定锚击",
              "type": "item",
              "entries": [
                "直到你的下一回合结束前，目标无法传送或进行位面旅行，包括进入异次元空间或半位面。"
              ]
            },
            {
              "ENG_name": "Banishing Strike",
              "name": "放逐击",
              "type": "item",
              "entries": [
                "目标传送至多15尺至一处你可见的未占据空间。"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Seeker",
      "name": "探寻者",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 3,
      "header": 1,
      "entries": [
        "你始终准备着{@spell 侦测魔法|XPHB}和{@spell 通晓语言|XPHB}法术。通过此特性，你可以不消耗法术位且无需材料成分地施展其中一个法术，且使用感知作为你的施法属性。",
        "一旦你用此特性施展了法术，除非消耗1点功力（无需动作）来恢复使用次数，否则你要完成一次{@variantrule 长休|XPHB}后才能再次以此方式施法。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Warden of Harmony",
      "name": "均衡执守",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 6,
      "header": 2,
      "entries": [
        "当60尺内的生物尝试传送时，你可以使用一个{@variantrule 反应|XPHB}并消耗1点功力来阻止该传送。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Cosmic Restoration",
      "name": "寰宇复元",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 11,
      "header": 2,
      "entries": [
        "以一个{@variantrule 附赠动作|XPHB}，你可以触碰一个自愿的生物（可以是你自己）并选择以下选项之一：",
        {
          "ENG_name": "Dispelling Touch",
          "name": "祛法触",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "你终止目标身上任意你选择的所有法术效果。"
          ]
        },
        {
          "ENG_name": "Purging Touch",
          "name": "净邪触",
          "type": "entries",
          "entries": [
            "你移除目标身上的以下状态之一：{@condition 目盲|XPHB}、{@condition 魅惑|XPHB}、{@condition 耳聋|XPHB}、{@condition 力竭|XPHB}（减少1级）、{@condition 恐慌|XPHB}、{@condition 麻痹|XPHB}、{@condition 石化|XPHB}、{@condition 中毒|XPHB}或{@condition 震慑|XPHB}。",
            "一旦你使用了此特性，则直至你完成一次{@variantrule 长休|XPHB}前，都无法再次使用。你也可以消耗4点功力（无需动作）来复原使用次数。"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "ENG_name": "Ward the Profane",
      "name": "邪祟封禁",
      "source": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "page": 0,
      "className": "武僧",
      "classSource": "XPHB",
      "subclassShortName": "天衡",
      "subclassSource": "CthulhuTorchlight",
      "level": 17,
      "header": 2,
      "entries": [
        "每回合一次，当你以{@variantrule 徒手打击|XPHB}命中一个生物时，你可以消耗3点功力以对该生物施放{@spell 放逐术|XPHB}。你使用感知作为此法术的施法属性。"
      ]
    }
  ],
